James Duffy

James is a postgraduate student at Imperial who is eager to drive positive social change through investment. He has a strong foundation in data analytics and sustainability research. Committed to leveraging finance to address global climate change, James loves to talk about impact investment, ESG, climate policy, transition risk, and renewable infrastructure investment.
